OL,3,CFour men jailed for 'brazen' daylight
OL,4,Ckidnapping
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed after a
OL,7,Fvictim was kidnapped and assaulted in
OL,8,FBrighton.
OL,10,FIt happened on November 5 2022, just
OL,11,Fbefore 4pm in the Whitehawk area of
OL,12,Fthe city. Emergency services received
OL,13,Freports that a 46 year old man was
OL,14,Fbeing assaulted and dragged into a car
OL,15,Fon Chiddingly Close.
OL,17,FShortly afterwards, the same victim
OL,18,Fwas found in North Drive with his
OL,19,Fhands tied behind his back.
