OL,6,FHis clothing was ripped, bleached and
OL,7,Fstained, and a strong smell of bleach
OL,8,Flingered over him. He had suffered a
OL,9,Fsustained physical assault and was
OL,10,Fgiven medical treatment.
OL,12,FSussex Police linked this violent
OL,13,Fincident to two burglaries: one in
OL,14,FSheridan Terrace, Hove, and another in
OL,15,FBedford Square, Brighton ` both
OL,16,Faddresses connected to the victim.
OL,18,FA rented van seen near the kidnapping
OL,19,Fscene was investigated, and officers
OL,20,Ffound balaclavas, saws and knives -
OL,21,Fall swabbed for DNA.
