OL,6,FFollowing arrests between November
OL,7,F2022 and early 2023, charges were
OL,8,Fbrought in July 2024.
OL,10,FThe four men ` Stephen Marsh (42),
OL,11,FWilliam Westein (29), Harry Avis (27),
OL,12,Fand Regan White (22) ` were found
OL,13,Fguilty of kidnap, false imprisonment,
OL,14,Fburglary and grievous bodily harm with
OL,15,Fintent after a three-week trial at
OL,16,FHove Crown Court in early 2025.
OL,18,FOn October 17 , the four men were
OL,19,Fsentenced to:
