OL,6,FCriminal Investigations Detective
OL,7,FSergeant, Charles Lawrence, said "this
OL,8,Fbrazen daylight kidnapping in Brighton
OL,9,Fhas led to four men receiving
OL,10,Fsubstantial prison sentences.
OL,12,F"Each offender played a significant
OL,13,Frole in inflicting serious harm and
OL,14,Fdistress on the victim, who
OL,15,Fconsequently sustained injuries from
OL,16,Fhead to toe.
